"{\"uid\": \"rappler.com-philippines-visayas-iloilo-health-officials-flak-use-carlos-yulo-paris-olympics-wins-offer-free-vasectomies\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  SUMMARY  This is AI generated summarization, which may have errors.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 69, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9954534818860512, \"rank\": 0.0045542295639777, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For context, always refer to the full article.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CONTROVERSIAL.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Iloilo Provincial Health Office's controversial vasectomy ad which stirred a controversy.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"score\": 0.9999987301306523, \"rank\": 1.2697754182934587e-06, \"text\": \"Iloilo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The local health office the Facebook post after it started a wave of negative reactions.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Deleted IPHO FB post  BACOLOD, Philippines - Health officials in Iloilo province have stirred controversy by usingFilipino gymnast Carlos Yuloand his two-gold-medal victories in the Paris Olympics to promote their family planning and vasectomy campaign.\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6481808689372754e-16, \"text\": \"BACOLOD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.438564113812492e-18, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"score\": 0.9999987301306523, \"rank\": 1.2697754182934587e-06, \"text\": \"Iloilo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using Yulo as the poster boy for a social media ad campaign, the Iloilo Provincial Health Office (IPHO) offered Ilonggo males a quick and minimally invasive procedure for permanent male contraception, which does not require stitches and has a faster recovery time.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"score\": 0.9999987301306523, \"rank\": 1.2697754182934587e-06, \"text\": \"Iloilo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\"}, {\"begin\": 684, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ad triumphantly read, \\\"Congratulations, Caloy!\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To celebrate your victory in the Paris 2024 Olympics, the Iloilo PHO will offer free vasectomies to all Ilonggos named 'Carlos,' including their friends!\\\"\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The campaign, dubbed \\\"Panalo si Carlos Yulo, Panalo ang Pamilyang Planado!\\\"\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"quickly made the rounds on social media, where it was greeted with a chorus of jeers, laughter, and bewilderment.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Many netizens were quick to point out the irony of choosing a young and unmarried athlete as a model forvasectomy, a procedure which involves a small incision in the scrotum to close off the tubes that carry sperm.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"netizens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The backlash was swift and fierce, prompting the IPHO to delete the post as it quickly spread and generated a flood of negative and nasty comments, with some going to the extent of unfairly playing into stereotypes about Ilonggo males.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IPHO replaced it with another ad.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Maria Socorro Colmenares-Qui\\u00f1on, in a statement published by the Iloilo-basedDaily Guardian, noted that while the campaign did attract interest from at least 15 eager Ilonggo males immediately, it also generated many negative reactions.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"score\": 0.9999561164320157, \"rank\": 3.8238483278664045e-05, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\", \"score\": 0.6222965234602363, \"rank\": 0.5683940474298003, \"text\": \"Socorro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\"}, {\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were also negative interpretations, which we cannot control anymore,\\\" Qui\\u00f1on said.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the backlash, the Department of Health (DOH) on Wednesday, August 7, gave a nod of approval to the IPHO's brief but controversial vasectomy ad.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Health Undersecretary Mary Ann Palermo-Maestral said, \\\"We commend IPHO's creativity for capitalizing on thepopularity of Yulo\\u2026 just to boost its campaign for free-scalpel vasectomy aimed at enticing Ilonggo family men to submit to this minimally invasive family planning procedure.It actually matters nowadays, especially that August is a Family Planning Month.\\\"\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2235, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7446480677569085, \"rank\": 0.17739977524412054, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}, {\"begin\": 2334, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maestral said Yulo's popularity might be the perfect \\\"sailing point\\\" for the IPHO to navigate the choppy waters of promoting vasectomies among Ilonggo family men.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday night, the IPHO released an official statement to express its \\\"sincerest apologies for the recent social media ad campaign.\\\"\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was never our intention to misrepresent Mr. Yulo or imply any personal endorsement from him.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2928, \"end\": 2932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We recognize that our choice of imagery was inappropriate and may have caused confusion and offense.\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We deeply respect Mr. Yulo's achievements and his contributions to sports, and did not seek to undermine his personal or professional image in any way\\u2026.\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We sincerely apologize to Mr. Yulo, his family, and all those who were affected by our actions,\\\" read part of the statement.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3261, \"end\": 3265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IPHO also reiterated its commitment to promoting public health initiatives with sensitivity and respect towards people.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As we strive to improve our communication strategies, we will ensure that our future campaigns are conducted with the utmost care and consideration,\\\" the IPHO said.\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"-Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": []}]}"